"title": "7241: Jerusalem, significance of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7241",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Chosen by God as the location for his sanctuary, Jerusalem was his symbolic dwelling and became the only acceptable place for sacrificial worship. It retained its symbolic significance in NT times when it came to represent the hope of restoration and renewal for the people of God.</p>\n<h2>Jerusalem chosen by God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:32\">1KI 11:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:44-1Kgs8:51\">1KI 8:44–8:51</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:34-2Chr6:39\">2CH 6:34–6:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:36\">1KI 11:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:21\">1KI 14:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:13\">2CH 12:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:27\">2KI 23:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:8-Neh1:9\">NEH 1:8–1:9</a></p>\n<h2>The ark of the covenant brought to Jerusalem</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:1-1Chr15:3\">1CH 15:1–15:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:1-2Sam6:19\">2SA 6:1–6:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:25-1Chr16:3\">1CH 15:25–16:3</a></p>\n<h2>The temple located in Jerusalem</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:1\">2CH 3:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr6:31-1Chr6:32\">1CH 6:31–6:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:27-2Chr20:28\">2CH 20:27–20:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:7\">2CH 33:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:14\">2CH 36:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:22-2Chr36:23\">2CH 36:22–36:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra1:1-Ezra1:3\">EZR 1:1–1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:28-Ps68:29\">PSA 68:28–68:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:11\">MRK 11:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:15-Mark11:16\">MRK 11:15–11:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:41-Luke2:51\">LUK 2:41–2:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:9\">LUK 4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:13-Acts22:18\">ACT 22:13–22:18</a></p>\n<h2>Jerusalem the only acceptable place for sacrificial worship</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:1-Deut12:7\">DEU 12:1–12:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:20-Deut12:28\">DEU 12:20–12:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:26-1Kgs13:3\">1KI 12:26–13:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:22-1Kgs14:24\">1KI 14:22–14:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:42-1Kgs22:43\">1KI 22:42–22:43</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:31-2Chr20:33\">2CH 20:31–20:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:1-2Kgs12:3\">2KI 12:1–12:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs16:1-2Kgs16:4\">2KI 16:1–16:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:1-2Chr28:4\">2CH 28:1–28:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:1-2Kgs23:20\">2KI 23:1–23:20</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:29-2Chr34:32\">2CH 34:29–34:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:1-2Chr31:1\">2CH 30:1–31:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:20\">ISA 66:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:8\">HOS 10:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:20-John4:21\">JHN 4:20–4:21</a></p>\n<h2>Jerusalem referred to as God's dwelling-place</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:21\">PSA 135:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:23\">ISA 24:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa31:9\">ISA 31:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:17\">JER 3:17</a></p>\n<h2>Personification of Jerusalem</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:1-Isa52:2\">ISA 52:1–52:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:12\">PSA 147:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:8\">ISA 3:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:2\">ISA 40:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:27\">ISA 41:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:9\">ISA 52:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:6-Isa62:7\">ISA 62:6–62:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:1-Jer2:2\">JER 2:1–2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:14\">JER 4:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:8\">JER 6:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:9\">JER 13:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:26-Jer13:27\">JER 13:26–13:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:5\">JER 15:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:17\">LAM 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:13-Lam2:15\">LAM 2:13–2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek5:8\">EZK 5:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:1-Ezek16:63\">EZK 16:1–16:63</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek23:1-Ezek23:49\">EZK 23:1–23:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:14-Zeph3:17\">ZEP 3:14–3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:9-Zech9:10\">ZEC 9:9–9:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:37-Matt23:39\">MAT 23:37–23:39</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:34-Luke13:35\">LUK 13:34–13:35</a></p>\n<h2>Jerusalem the place of Jesus Christ's triumphal entry</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:28-Luke19:38\">LUK 19:28–19:38</a></p>\n<h2>Jerusalem the place of Jesus Christ's death and resurrection</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:26-Luke23:49\">LUK 23:26–23:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:1-Luke24:12\">LUK 24:1–24:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:13-Luke24:33\">LUK 24:13–24:33</a></p>\n<h2>The outpouring of the Holy Spirit in Jerusalem</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:4-Acts1:9\">ACT 1:4–1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:1-Acts2:21\">ACT 2:1–2:21</a></p>\n<h2>Jerusalem the administrative centre of the church</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:1\">ACT 8:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:14\">ACT 8:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:25\">ACT 8:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:1-Acts11:22\">ACT 11:1–11:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:27\">ACT 11:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:25\">ACT 12:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:13\">ACT 13:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:1-Acts15:29\">ACT 15:1–15:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:4\">ACT 16:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:1-1Cor16:3\">1CO 16:1–16:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:15-Gal1:19\">GAL 1:15–1:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:1-Gal2:10\">GAL 2:1–2:10</a></p>\n<h2>The new Jerusalem</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:1-Rev21:5\">REV 21:1–21:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek48:30-Ezek48:35\">EZK 48:30–48:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:25-Gal4:26\">GAL 4:25–4:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:18-Heb12:24\">HEB 12:18–12:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:11-Rev3:13\">REV 3:11–3:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:9-Rev21:27\">REV 21:9–21:27</a></p>",
